Which culture developed the first writing system in the Western Hemisphere?
<list id="eip-idm558112832" list-type="enumerated" number-style="upper-alpha"><item>Inca</item>
<item>Maya</item>
<item>Olmec</item>
<item>Pueblo</item>
</list></para>
</problem>

<solution id="eip-67">
